 <tr><TD bgcolor='#003366' width='655'><B><FONT face='Verdana' color=#ffffff size=3>&nbsp;&nbsp;So sue me...</font></b>&nbsp;&nbsp;<font face='Verdana' size='-7' color='#FFFF00'>  Rombus ~  Wednesday October 17th, 2001</font></td></tr>
	<tr><TD width=655 align='left'><font face='Verdana'><p><font size=2 face=Verdana>Well, two hard drive formats and
about 50 uber mobs later, I RETURN! Yes, that's right, now you
can all stop harassing me to update. There's been a
lot of changes in EQ over the past couple of weeks. Melees got
huge damage upgrades and Necros can now nuke mobs. That's
actually what I want to talk about. Can we please nerf Necros
back to being my fucking mana battery? Seriously! I've put up
with them being able to nuke for two god damn weeks, I've had
about enough.</font></p>
<div align=center><center>

<table border=0>
    <tr>
        <td><img src=images/news/17october01/ladymirskelly.jpg
        width=200 height=200></td>
        <td><img src=images/news/17october01/lordkioskelly.jpg
        width=200 height=200></td>
        <td><img
        src=images/news/17october01/kingtormaxskelly.jpg
        width=200 height=200></td>
    </tr>
</table>
</center></div>

<p><font size=2 face=Verdana>Brownivy, Minael ... ... Zaar
... It sickens me to see 'a_Triton_necro03 radiates with essence'
on a raid. It sickens me to see you refuse to feed me mana
when I'm out. FFS know your place and twitch me, bitch!</font></p>

<p><font size=2 face=Verdana>Onto the good stuff!
Yesterday night Triton was forced into Kael in search the elusive
Statue of Rallos Zek. We were hoping we might get a first hand
look at the 'Mystical Blade of the Reaver' and possible obtain
one of these rare artifacts for our main tanks. Using deployment
method 'Triton Beta Two Druid Alpha' we were able to destroy the
Statue's worthless guardian, Vindicator. He dropped a Breastplate
for Gaven who quickly destroyed his Rune Etched (fag!).</font></p>

<table border=0>
    <tr>
        <td valign=middle><font size=2 face=Verdana><img
        src=images/news/17october01/statuecorpse.jpg
        width=420 height=194></font></td>
        <td><font size=2 face=Verdana>While preparing for the
        Statue we were suddenly greeted by our characters hurling
        weapons around. That's right, the god damn zone crashed,
        THX VI! Deja Vu, Hail, Derekor the Vindicator! Oh well,
        time to die. We killed him and he actually dropped *gasp*
        AN EARRING OF LIGHTNING! Triton's first earring went to
        Bentos. On a side note, Vindicator died in skelly form
        (FIJ:LSDKJF*(#*)*@)(# F FUCKING NECROS!).</font><p><font
        size=2 face=Verdana>Finally, the Statue was quickly
        destroyed resulting in a Hammer of Battle for Moran, a
        Cloak of Falling Stars for Analon (whoops!), and an Iron
        Scroll of War for Heatstorm (don't pull a
        Mardigann/Elrood that thing!).</font></p>
        </td>
    </tr>
</table>

<p align=center><font size=2 face=Verdana>-- INSERT
MEANINGLESS FEAR CLEARING WITH CT DEAD RESULTING IN TWO PAULDRONS
(ARMA/DREADWAR) AND A CHOKER (DUNRIC) AND A VINDI DEATH RESULTING
IN BOOTS (FROSST) HERE --</font></p>

<p><font size=2 face=Verdana>We went to VP this
weekend and dropped Phara Dar, Hoshkar, Nexona, and Xygoz.
Nothing of note really except for a Shield of Elders for Boken, a
Shroud of Veeshan for Nurben (go Ice), a Staff of the Null for
Zorulis (!!!), and...</font></p>

<p align=center><font size=5 face=Verdana><strong>A DMF
ROBE FOR MINAEL FUCK YOU NEXONA #16!!!</strong></font></p>

<p><font size=2 face=Verdana>Oh yes, for those of you who
aren't convinced that Triton is the evil devil of Povar, you
should let Narya tell you the story about how we ran over her
guild's first VP trip and let the 23 of them there team up with
us for PD and Hoshkar resulting in them getting 2/3 Hoshkar loots
and two Shield of the Elders that our Clerics could have used. My
god, we're such evil bastards. By the way Narya, Nurben LOVES his
Shroud! Keep in mind that this entire thing could have been
avoided if you guys had told us about your VP trip like we asked
you to last month. You know we do VP <strong>monthly</strong>, is
it that hard to tell us when you're planning to? Innit did! </font></p>

<p><font size=2 face=Verdana>Send hate mail for that one to </font><a
href=mailto:dialtone@adelphia.net><font size=2 face=Verdana>dialtone@adelphia.net</font></a><font
size=2 face=Verdana>~</font></p>

<p><font size=2 face=Verdana>*yawns* I'm such a lazy bastard.
I can't believe I let the site go this long without an update. </font></p>

<p><font size=2 face=Verdana>Let's see, what's next on this
stupid list of things we did...</font></p>

