<p><font size=2 face=Verdana>That just about does it for this
update. Sorry it was so late, but two formats in one week sucks.
;) </font></p>

<p><font size=2 face=Verdana>A bunch of people have asked if Triton is playing DAoC. The answer is no. About five of
us have bought the game and most of us were in beta and ended up
hating it. Sorry Mythic, this isn't the EQ killer we expected. If
you see a Rombus in DAoC, that's not me. Hell, if you see a
Rombus on any server but Povar chances are it's not me. To the
fag who is using my name to try and get stuff from people on
other servers: FUCK OFF.</font></p>

